MIME media type name : Application

MIME subtype name : Vendor Tree - vnd.audiograph

Required parameters : 


Optional parameters : 


Encoding considerations : 
8 bit raw binary data


Security considerations : 

There are no security risks involved.

This type of file describes a sort of 'vector' movie. It also contains
PNG image data and GSM sound data. It cannot be used in any way to
gain control of a remote system.


Interoperability considerations : 
Usage on MacOS, Windows95 and WindowsNT.
Future usage on Rhapsody and Unix.


Published specification : 
Confidential Specification at this moment


Applications which use this media : 
AudioGraph Plugin for Netscape (MacOS) uses this media type
AudioGraph Plugin for Netscape (MacOS) uses this media type
AudioGraph Plugin for Netscape (Windows95/WindowsNT) uses this media type
AudioGraph Player (MacOS) uses this media type
AudioGraph Recorder (MacOS) creates this media type
AudioGraph Recorder (Windows95/Windows95) creates this media type
